      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Sources</h2>
      <ul class="text-sm text-slate-500 space-y-1">
        <li>
          <a href="https://www.ncsl.org/elections-and-campaigns/vacancies-in-the-united-states-senate" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-dem hover:underline">National Conference of State Legislatures &mdash; Senate Vacancies</a>
        </li>
        <li>
