          <a href="https://ballotpedia.org/U.S._Congress_special_elections_historical_data,_1987-2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-dem hover:underline">Ballotpedia &mdash; U.S. Congress Special Elections Historical Data (1987&ndash;2024)</a>
        </li>
